      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Keyword: agentic memory",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "The taxonomy provides a treatment of **loop primitives** -- the control-flow building blocks (think/act/observe loops, plan-then-execute loops, reflexion loops, hierarchical sub-task loops) that scaffold the agent's outer reasoning cycle.",
      "content_hash": "1e9db86ce14c77ae78c4f03a8e20c5444c983f581bd2ebb8fc49efc23b94e20d",
      "declaration_index": 5,
