      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "Keyword: context compaction",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "The taxonomy provides a treatment of **tool capability categories** -- the classes of capabilities that coding-agent tools expose (file I/O, code search, edit/patch application, shell execution, test running, version control, browser/web access, ...) and how scaffolds organise and expose them.",
